    "chemicalDescription": [
      "sr-(s-Mussel Polypeptide-2 Dipeptide-40 Oligopeptide-233) is a single chain recombinant peptide, produced by fermentation in E. coli. The starting gene is synthesized by the fusion of the gene from s-Mussel Polypeptide-2, Dipeptide-40, and Oligopeptide-233. The fusion peptide contains 189 amino acids which may contain disulfide bonds and/or glycosylation, and consists of the proper sequence of the 20 standard amino acids."
    ],
